node.text:
Who loves a well-deserved surprise home makeover?! ✨ We teamed up with 15-time Grammy award winner @AliciaKeys to give back to a “Hometown Hero” in LA. 
 
Susanna, a rock star special education teacher at Van Nuys High School, has always put her students first. The COVID-19 pandemic didn’t change that, even after losing five family members in the same year. She worked tirelessly to support her students, their families, and her co-workers—all while she and her husband, also a teacher, helped their own two children adjust to remote learning. 
 
To celebrate Susanna, we gifted her a home makeover—inside *and* out, creating a welcoming oasis for her and her family to spend quality time and create lasting memories. ❤️
 
As part of the project, Amazon will complete Susanna’s Classroom Wish List to ensure she and her students are set up well for the year in the classroom. Additionally, Amazon is also making donations in honor of Susanna to some of the organizations close to @AliciaKeys’ heart: @keepachildalive, @yourmomcares, @breathewithmerevolution, and @untilfreedom.
 
Tap the link in our bio to read more about Susanna’s story and shop these scenes— and don’t miss our story to see photos of the full before and after transformation! 🏡 #AmazonHometownHeroes #AmazonHome #Amazon #founditonamazon
